{"tid":2274093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉寶琳站包圍站長 何梓聰及另一手足被裁定非法集結罪成 分別判監3及4個月","createTime":"2020-11-06T08:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T16:28:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c05f148b840725ea989b38d8520f7b7bbde99e10","tid":2274093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11083&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=70ba49a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11083</a><br />\n<br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#徐綺薇主任裁判官<br />\n#判刑 #0904寶琳<br />\n<br />\n何,鍾(22-23)🛑兩位已還押20日 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：非法集結<br />\n<br />\n案情：在2019年9月4日，近百名示威者湧入港鐵寶琳站，其中2名被告涉嫌包圍並推撞一名下班的港鐵男職員，使他倒地受傷。2名被告原本被控襲擊港鐵職員罪，控方後來申請將控罪修改為參與非法集結，指他們在港鐵寶琳站內與其他人士參與非法集結，即作出帶有威嚇性、挑撥性及侮辱性行為等，相當可能會破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - -<br />\n<br />\n【速報】<br />\n<br />\nD1: 監禁3個月🛑<br />\nD2: 監禁4個月🛑<br />\n<br />\nD1申請定罪上訴獲批，期間批准保釋✅"},{"pid":"420ef3e7723a971cc5b4114dc18146e2d5f69fb7","tid":2274093,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:02:45.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"b38d6cfdb13a09050578d5240db8417d5d61d651","tid":2274093,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee8fda85be1b109f4234905f78fc11721e699c6","tid":2274093,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e89c5d3e1d32e776fb67c313f375b4659fd0b11","tid":2274093,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d377b893785b79086531a105443b3dcc8ea2cb87","tid":2274093,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">死紅官</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4679c353e71b65214844a8255ac10d2a66d19a74","tid":2274093,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:35:40.000Z","msg":"自己插水砌唔入就砌非法集結"},{"pid":"0b613e6db91afcb03487eaed08190da9414ec179","tid":2274093,"uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d377b893785b79086531a105443b3dcc8ea2cb87","tid":2274093,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">死紅官</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:56:26.000Z","msg":"徐官平時做嘢都stick to the rules <br />\n不過判刑一向相對重手<br />\n加上上訴庭指引講到明非法集結要判阻嚇性刑罰<br />\n<blockquote>上訴庭法官潘兆初在判詞定下量刑指示，指若非法集結牽涉暴力行為是有預謀、人數眾多、暴力程度、規模、維時長短、暴力引致的財物及人身受傷的損失及玻、及犯案者角色及參予程度等，所以在確保公共秩序上，判刑必須具備阻嚇，監禁是合適刑期。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢之前嘅案：<br />\n<blockquote>徐綺薇發火命令警方案件主管站起身 怒斥警方永遠拖到最後才交文件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810141</a><br />\n<br />\n10月13日PopCorn商場案 官:法庭不會接受造成如此嚴重傷勢的拘捕行為 控方需向法庭提供解釋<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fDykNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fDykNS</a><br />\n<br />\n【大三罷】設計師襲警罪名不成立 訟費申請獲批<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2098052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2098052</a><br />\n<br />\n控方拒准女生簽守行為 異於同類案 官籲再考慮：看不到為何有分別<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992429</a><br />\n<br />\n售貨員協助掘磚人士搬磚 今判社會服務令100小時 並向康文署賠償316元<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2235028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2235028</a><br />\n<br />\n拒批警匿名 官：不能常規化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2025604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2025604</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fa58a2612d6a7e83c449ea830cdd0fc6f7b9d722","tid":2274093,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:04:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%B6%E7%90%B3%E7%AB%99%E5%85%A7%E6%8E%A8%E6%92%9E%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E7%AB%99%E9%95%B7-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-3-%E8%87%B3-4-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%AE%98-%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E9%81%B7%E6%80%92%E7%AB%99%E9%95%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E7%2590%25B3%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-3-%25E8%2587%25B3-4-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2581%25B7%25E6%2580%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=8fe4b24a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E7%2590%25B3%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-3-%25E8%2587%25B3-4-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2581%25B7%25E6%2580%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&h=40a56b